<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.9.2">
<l>kaḻiyāruṅ kaṉacaṅkaṅ kalanteṅkum niṟaintēṟi</l>
<l>vaḻiyāra muttīṉṟu vaḷaṅkoṭukkun tirunaṟaiyūr</l>
<l>paḻiyārum viṟalarakkaṉ parumuṭika ḷavaicitaṟa</l>
<l>aḻalāruñ caranturantā ṉaṭiyiṇaiyē yaṭaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In Tirunaṟaiyūr where heavy shells which fill the marshes,</l>
<l rend="indent">mixing together, amassing,</l>
<l>Piling up everywhere, producing pearls so that they fill the paths,</l>
<l rend="indent">bestow [their] riches,</l>
<l>O heart, take refuge at both feet of the one who shot arrows which spread fire,</l>
<l>To scatter the [ten] thick heads of the strong, guilty demon.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
